note = | By itself without colorants, this glaze is fairly clear, not
note = |perfectly transparent at cone 6-7 but becoming glass like at 8-9.
note = | It is smooth to the touch, pleasing to feel.  Very tolerant and
note = |forgiving.
note = | It is somewhat uninteresting by itself although it is as stable as
